              'descr' => '<p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">It has been a month since the information about the new strain of coronavirus became public.</p>

              <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Front pages of broadsheet newspapers and television screens have glaring images of facemasks worn by people in China. These single-use facemasks have spunmelt and carded filter substrates and have been in demand in China since the outbreak.</p>
              <figure style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 7px auto 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: block; clear: both; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; max-width: 100%; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; width: 640px;">
                <a href="https://www.textiletoday.com.bd/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Nonwoven-facemask-coronavirus-infection-containment.jpg" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(63, 81, 181);"><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" src="https://www.textiletoday.com.bd/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/Nonwoven-facemask-coronavirus-infection-containment.jpg" alt="Nonwoven-facemask-coronavirus-infection-containment" width="640" height="426"  style="box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; height: auto; max-width: 100%;" class="fr-fil fr-dib"></a>
                <figcaption style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; display: block; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4;">Figure:&nbsp;Nonwoven substrates play an important role in human health and environmental protection against the outbreak of coronavirus.</figcaption>
              </figure>

              <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">With the WHO&rsquo;s recent announcement that this outbreak is a global emergency, containment measures will get attention including vaccine development. As of yesterday, there have been 170 deaths in China due to this outbreak and the infection has spread to 18 countries.</p>

              <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">According to medical experts, a primary mode of spread of this new coronavirus is by transmission through air and are airborne. Good hygiene such as hand wash and protection are recommended. Facemasks can help with the containment of airborne infection depending on their level of protection. Nonwoven wipes can be a good aide for personnel hygiene.</p>

              <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">&ldquo;Filters will play a part in slowing or stopping the spread of the coronavirus in hospitals and other building that utilize high MERV 13 and above rated filters to remove the virus which is air borne from the air. Other filters include face masks which can stop the transmission of the virus through coughing and sneezing when other people are within a 3-6-foot radius,&rdquo; stated <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/christopherplotz/" rel="noopener" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(63, 81, 181);" target="_blank">Chris Plotz</a>, Director of Education &amp; Technical Affairs of INDA, a 19-year nonwoven industry veteran.</p>

              <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">According to Cary-based Association of Nonwoven Fabrics Industry (<a href="https://www.inda.org/" rel="noopener" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(63, 81, 181);" target="_blank">INDA</a>), filter and wipes substrates have 25% share based on weight, collectively at the end-user level. Overall, at the producer (roll goods) level, the industry is valued at US$15.5 billion.</p>

              <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Nonwoven substrates play an important role in human health and environmental protection. In recent times, when toxic chemical attacks happened, FiberTect decontamination wipes marketed by Chantilly-based First Line Technology proved its usefulness. After the 2010 BP oil spill in the United States, several nonwoven wipe technologies emerged. <a href="https://towelieglobal.com/" rel="noopener" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(63, 81, 181);" target="_blank">Towelie&trade;</a> an environmentally friendly nonwoven-based oil absorbent technology evolved. In hospitals, while treating infected personnel, caregivers use different types of PPEs.</p>

              <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Nonwoven and textile products rise up to the occasion and aide with the containment of infectious disease outbreaks and environmental problems such as crude oil spills.</p>',
              'status' => '10',
              'is_article' => '1'
            ],

            [
              'id' => '8',
              'user_id' => '3',
              'post_type_id' => '1',
              'title' => 'China’s AI-based technology for virtual fabric samples to cut production costs by 70%',
              'descr' => '<p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><a href="https://heartdub.com/" rel="noopener" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(63, 81, 181);" target="_blank">Heartdub&reg;</a>, a multinational AI Chinese startup, is primarily involved in the fashion industry that has recently developed a technology to provide virtual fabric samples to clothing manufacturers.</p>
                <figure style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 7px auto 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: block; clear: both; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; max-width: 100%; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; width: 640px;">
                  <a href="https://www.textiletoday.com.bd/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Heartdub-AI-based-technology-virtual-fabric-samples.jpg" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(63, 81, 181);"><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" src="https://www.textiletoday.com.bd/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Heartdub-AI-based-technology-virtual-fabric-samples.jpg" alt="Heartdub AI-based technology, virtual fabric samples" width="640" height="356" srcset="https://www.textiletoday.com.bd/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Heartdub-AI-based-technology-virtual-fabric-samples.jpg 640w, https://www.textiletoday.com.bd/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Heartdub-AI-based-technology-virtual-fabric-samples-300x167.jpg 300w, https://www.textiletoday.com.bd/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Heartdub-AI-based-technology-virtual-fabric-samples-585x325.jpg 585w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" style="box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; height: auto; max-width: 100%;" class="fr-fil fr-dib"></a>
                  <figcaption style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; display: block; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4;">Figure: HeartDub&rsquo;s platform is composed of a materials database, design images and images of sample clothes worn by a virtual model. Courtesy: HeartDub</figcaption>
                </figure>

                <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Fashion brands also need to make fewer samples of clothing because they can see how they will look, thanks to the virtual models. Production costs can be cut by 70% and sample delivery time is shortened by 90%.</p>

                <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">The software gathers data on textile materials and generates virtual fabrics that imitate the properties of the real garment fabric. The startup&rsquo;s goal is to digitize logistics in the apparel industry and provide online solutions for the development and selection of textile materials, and the production of clothing samples.</p>

                <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">HeartDub&rsquo;s platform includes a materials database, design images and simulated images of clothes worn by virtual models. The database comprises information on various fabrics, patterns and colors. Designs are created by combining them, and the digital clothes put on a virtual model programmed to make various body movements to show how they would look in real life.</p>

                <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Li Ruohao, the company&rsquo;s Chief Technology Officer, informs that virtual fabric-making starts with analyzing the structure of actual fabrics and inputting the data into the software, called a &lsquo;physics-engine,&rsquo; to simulate a fabric&rsquo;s physical properties. HeartDub&rsquo;s laboratory already has extensive data on frequently used fabrics. The characteristics of these virtual fabrics correspond to those in the real world. Allowing their texture, weight and movements to be accurately simulated.</p>

                <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">HeartDub&reg;&rsquo;s main customers are fabric makers and fashion brands. Manufacturers upload newly developed textiles to the platform. Fashion labels then select the texture, pattern, and design online. After examining how the clothing looks on virtual models, they decide whether to purchase the fabric.</p>

                <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Li Ruohao said, &ldquo;The company&rsquo;s digital platform allows fabric makers to complete the steps up to a preorder presentation at no cost, thereby cutting their overall development cost by about half.&rdquo;</p>

                <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Virtual fashion shows in the future will provide an opportunity for businesses to showcase new products, transforming the apparel industry into a digital one with the potential for sustainable growth.</p>

                <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">HeartDub&reg; aims to unleash the next generation of neural network-powered technology and bring sustainable fashion to an entirely new level of experience. Its commitment is to excellence drives in every aspect of the operation process. With the world&rsquo;s best and brightest minds, the company accomplishes things that were never before possible.</p>
                ',
              'status' => '10',
              'is_article' => '1'
            ],

            [
              'id' => '9',
              'user_id' => '3',
              'post_type_id' => '1',
              'title' => 'IMB is the industry 4.0 solution for BD apparel makers',
              'descr' => '<p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><a href="http://www.imb-china.com/en.php/index/index.html" rel="noopener" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(63, 81, 181);" target="_blank">IMB</a>, a specialized company of automated machinery manufacturing for apparel making, organized a networking grooming session for Bangladeshi RMG manufacturers at Uttara Club, Dhaka on 16 January 2020.</p>
                <figure style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 7px auto 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: block; clear: both; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; max-width: 100%; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; width: 640px;">
                  <a href="https://www.textiletoday.com.bd/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/IMB-sewing-@-Uttara.jpg" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: transparent; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(63, 81, 181);"><img src="https://www.textiletoday.com.bd/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/IMB-sewing-@-Uttara.jpg" alt="IMB sewing @ Uttara" width="640" height="426" style="box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; height: auto; max-width: 100%;" class="fr-fil fr-dib"></a>
                  <figcaption style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; display: block; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4;">Figure 1: (From left, front row) Rafael, Sales Manager; Sreedam Bhattacharjee Sumon, Country Manager; Johan Grieten, Global Sales Director; Chen Xin Hua, Chairman; Shaheda Akter Neelu, Country Director.</figcaption>
                </figure>

                <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Chairman of IMB Chen Xin Hua started the event with his dynamic team member where Johan Grieten, Global Sales Director and R&amp;D Adviser of IMB; Rafael, Sales Manager; Shaheda Akter Neelu, Country Director; &nbsp;Sreedam Bhattacharya Sumon, Country Manager were present.</p>

                <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">They promised Bangladeshi apparel manufacturers to attain a long-term achievement target in their demand and production.</p>

                <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">Many renowned apparel manufacturers of Bangladesh were present at the event to look for industry solutions from IMB.</p>

                <p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">IMB was set up in 2013 with 220 staff, including 30 R&amp;D technicians. 8% of their sales is used for R&amp;D yearly. Before starting IMB, Chen has been cooperated with BROTHER company for 25 years since 1995 as a BROTHER company China top one dealer.</p>

